OL,6,FMr Hall said the payments may come too
OL,7,Flate for some: "They are extremely
OL,8,Fimportant for a lot of people who were
OL,9,Fseriously ill. And as we know, that's
OL,10,Fup to two people dying every week. And
OL,11,Fmany, many people are going to die
OL,12,Fbefore the end of the year, and they
OL,13,Fmay die without receiving any
OL,14,Fcompensation."
