OL,4,Crather have 'a healthy life' than money
OL,6,FFollowing his life in treatment for
OL,7,Fliver cancer and requiring a
OL,8,Ftransplant, Mr Hall continued, "I
OL,9,Fdon't think there actually is any
OL,10,Famount of money that can compensate
OL,11,Ffor that. I think most people would
OL,12,Fmuch rather have a healthy life than
OL,13,Fthe money."
OL,15,FMr Hall's wife is also entitled to
OL,16,Fcompensation.
