OL,4,Crather have 'a healthy life' than money
OL,6,F"They insisted on waiting for the
OL,7,Ffinal report, and I don't know why
OL,8,Fthey were insistent waiting for the
OL,9,Ffinal report. And that didn't wait for
OL,10,Fthe inquiry into Post Office Scandal
OL,11,Fto complete and never mind a final
OL,12,Freport from that before announcing
OL,13,Fcompensation for the post office.
OL,15,F"I actually wrote a letter to
OL,16,F(Paymaster General) John Glenn asking
OL,17,Fthat question. I haven't received a
OL,18,Freply yet from John Glenn."
