OL,3,CInfected Blood Scandal: Man would
OL,4,Crather have 'a healthy life' than money
OL,6,FIt was announced on Tuesday 21 May,
OL,7,Fthat anyone already registered with
OL,8,Fsupport schemes will in the government-
OL,9,Frun scheme.
OL,11,FAll those affected by the scandal -
OL,12,Fnot only those who were infected with
OL,13,Fcontaminated blood - will receive
OL,14,Fpayouts, he confirmed, listing
OL,15,Fpartners, parents, siblings, children,
OL,16,Ffamily and friends.
OL,18,FThe government confirmed non-taxable
OL,19,Fcompensation for victims who have died
OL,20,Fwithout seeing justice will go to
OL,21,Ftheir estate.
