OL,6,FAsked how the compensation will
OL,7,Fbenefit his family, Mr Hall said: "It
OL,8,Fjust gives you that sense of security
OL,9,Fand redress because of everything that
OL,10,Fyou've gone through, the life that
OL,11,Fyou've had of constant worry.
OL,13,FIt just rights some of those wrongs
OL,14,Fand it needs to happen, especially for
OL,15,Fpeople who suffered financial
OL,16,Fhardship, people who were infected
OL,17,Fwith HIV or family members who were
OL,18,Finfected with HIV, with the stigma
OL,19,Fattached to HIV.
