OL,6,F"There's a lot of people who were not
OL,7,Fallowed to work. They had to take
OL,8,Fcareer breaks. They had to change the
OL,9,Fcareer that they might have had to a
OL,10,Fcareer that gave them more time off to
OL,11,Flook after people. And I think the
OL,12,Fcompensation is to cover that as well."
